Insider Activity


Individual




Gregg G. Williams



Mr. Gregg G. Williams is Independent Director at Second Sight Medical Products, Inc. and Chief Executive Officer at Williams International Co. LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Second Sight Medical Products, Inc. and General Aviation Manufacturers Association.
Mr. Williams was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Williams International Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Utah.



