Greg Williams is the Vice President of Product Management and leads product development across the Tempest publishing platform and Say Media’s advertising technology stack. Prior to Say Media, Greg worked at Boeing, NASA, Apple and Meraki in various engineering, operations and product management roles. He holds an MBA and engineering master’s degree from MIT and a bachelor’s degree in mechanical engineering from Cornell University.



